snippet.title: webon
snippet.description: webon is a web-site managing project for web-site owners. webon uses PHP5(only 5 and not 4) and POSTGRESQL, which is fast and secure. With webon web-site owners can easily create and maintain web-pages with less effort and with much satisfaction.

snippet.title: pyCRM
snippet.description: pyCRM puts together some basic building stones of each CRM like user administration, calendars etc. The main intention is to provide some metadata driven system to simplify extensibility and upgradeability of CRM systems built on top of it.
